  Locus:
    Page: 1035
Tags:
  - Invocation=The Glory of the Name
By: Muhammad
---
Whenever men gather together to invoke Allâh, they are surrounded by Angels,
the Divine Favour envelops them, and Peace (as-sakmah) descends upon them,
and Allâh remembers them in His assembly.
